properties.Name: Brunswick Rd "Dedicated Lanes" have cars parked in them
properties.description:
- There are no Dedicated Lanes on Brunswick Rd between Truscott St and Stranger St.
- There is a wide parking lane but most of the extra space is in the door zone
- Most of this section should not be marked with any bike infra as the speed limit is 60km/hr and better routes exist
- Better adjacent routes are the Capital City Trail and Barkly St
